OL,3,CFloyd Mayweather to come out of
OL,4,Cretirement for Manny Pacquiao rematch
OL,6,FFloyd Mayweather and Manny Pacquiao
OL,7,Fare set to face each other in a
OL,8,Frematch in Las Vegas later this year.
OL,10,FOver a decade on from their first
OL,11,Fbout, the two boxers will renew their
OL,12,Frivalry at an event hosted at the
OL,13,FSphere on September 19.
OL,15,FMayweather claimed a unanimous points
OL,16,Fwin when the two met in 2015, also in
OL,17,FLas Vegas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
