OL,3,CFloyd Mayweather to come out of
OL,4,Cretirement for Manny Pacquiao rematch
OL,6,FThe event, promoted as the 'Fight of
OL,7,Fthe Century', was the sport's highest
OL,8,Fgrossing, generating revenue reported
OL,9,Fto be in the region of #445 million.
OL,11,FBut boxing has changed significantly
OL,12,Fsince the 2015 event, which at the
OL,13,Ftime faced criticism for coming too
OL,14,Flate in both boxer's careers.
OL,16,FMayweather, now 49 years old, has not
OL,17,Fhad a professional boxing fight since
OL,18,Fhe defeated Conor McGregor in 2017.
OL,19,FThis victory extended his record to 50-
OL,20,F0.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
