OL,3,CFloyd Mayweather to come out of
OL,4,Cretirement for Manny Pacquiao rematch
OL,6,F"I already fought and beat Manny once.
OL,7,FThis time will be the same result,"
OL,8,Fthe undefeated boxer said.
OL,10,FPacquiao, 47, drew against
OL,11,Fwelterweight champion Mario Barrios in
OL,12,FJuly. Prior to this, his last
OL,13,Fprofessional bout came in 2021.
OL,15,FHe has 62 wins from his 73 bouts and
OL,16,Fis the only boxer to win world titles
OL,17,Fin eight different divisions.
OL,19,F"Floyd and I gave the world what
OL,20,Fremains the biggest fight in boxing
OL,21,Fhistory," Pacquiao said.
