OL,3,CFloyd Mayweather to come out of
OL,4,Cretirement for Manny Pacquiao rematch
OL,6,F"The fans have waited long enough`they
OL,7,Fdeserve this rematch, and it will be
OL,8,Feven bigger now that it will be
OL,9,Fstreamed live globally on Netflix.
OL,11,F"I want Floyd to live with the one
OL,12,Floss on his professional record and
OL,13,Falways remember who gave it to him.
OL,15,F"As always, I dedicate this fight to
OL,16,Fmy fellow Filipinos around the world
OL,17,Fand to bringing glory to the
OL,18,FPhilippines."
