OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FMayweather has been scheduled to first
OL,12,Fface former heavyweight champion Mike
OL,13,FTyson in an exhibition bout,
OL,14,Freportedly in the Democratic Republic
OL,15,Fof Congo, on April 25.
OL,17,FThis event may be delayed due to the
OL,18,Flatest announcement.
